// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Mappings used exclusively by PK-auto-inference tests (testAutoInferPK*).
// Each one binds a class to a pkTest* relation function. Property mappings
// are intentionally minimal and only reference columns that survive the
// corresponding relation pipeline (e.g. for select(~[AGE, FIRMID]) we only
// map age + firmId because ID, FIRST NAME and SALARY are projected away).
// id 'pk' is reused everywhere because pkOf() looks the set impl up by id.
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

